    "mt2": "This book contains the account of God revealing to Habakkuk that what God does is good. We call this book",
    "mt1": "Habakkuk"
  ],
  "contents": [
    "c": "1",
    "style": "p",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "I am",
    "text": "I am",
    "text": " Habakkuk, a prophet. This is the ",
    "add": "message that Yahweh",
    "text": "message that Yahweh",
    "text": " gave to me in a vision.",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "Habakkuk\u2019s first complaint",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "I said,",
    "text": "I said,",
    "text": " \u201CYahweh, how long must I continue to call ",
    "add": "to you",
    "text": "to you",
    "text": " for help",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "before you respond?",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "I cry out to you ",
    "add": "for help",
    "text": "for help",
    "text": ", saying that ",
    "add": "people are acting",
    "text": "people are acting",
    "text": " violently ",
    "add": "everywhere",
    "text": "everywhere",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "but you do not rescue us!",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "3",
    "text": "\u25C4Must I/I do not want to\u25BA continue seeing people doing what is unjust [RHQ].",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "Why do you not punish people who are doing what is wrong [RHQ]?",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "I see people destroying things and ",
    "add": "acting",
    "text": "acting",
    "text": " violently.",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "There is fighting and quarreling ",
    "add": "everywhere",
    "text": "everywhere",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "4",
    "text": "No one obeys laws [PRS],",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and judges [PRS] never do what is fair/just.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Wicked people always defeat righteous people ",
    "add": "in the courts",
    "text": "in the courts",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "with the result that matters are never decided fairly/justly.\u201D",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "Yahweh\u2019s reply",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "5",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "Yahweh replied to me,",
    "text": "Yahweh replied to me,",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\u201C",
    "add": "I know that what you say is true, but",
    "text": "I know that what you say is true, but",
    "text": " look around at ",
    "add": "what is happening in",
    "text": "what is happening in",
    "text": " the other nations;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "if you look,",
    "text": "if you look,",
    "text": " you will be amazed,",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "because I am doing something during this time that you would not believe ",
    "add": "would happen",
    "text": "would happen",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "even if someone told you about it.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "6",
    "text": "The soldiers of Babylonia are fierce/cruel and swift.",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "And now I am causing them ",
    "add": "to become very powerful",
    "text": "to become very powerful",
    "text": ";",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "they will march across the world",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and conquer ",
    "add": "many",
    "text": "many",
    "text": " other countries.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "7",
    "text": "They are people whom ",
    "add": "others",
    "text": "others",
    "text": " fear very much [DOU],",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and they do whatever they want to,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "paying no attention to the laws of other countries.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "8",
    "text": "The horses ",
    "add": "that pull their chariots",
    "text": "that pull their chariots",
    "text": " go faster than leopards,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and they are fiercer than wolves are in the evening.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "The horses on which the soldiers ride gallop swiftly;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "the soldiers riding them come from distant places.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "They are like [SIM] eagles that swoop down to ",
    "add": "snatch and",
    "text": "snatch and",
    "text": " kill small animals.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "9",
    "text": "As they ride along,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "they are",
    "text": "they are",
    "text": " determined to act violently.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "They advance like [SIM] a wind from the desert,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "gathering prisoners that are as ",
    "add": "numerous as grains of",
    "text": "numerous as grains of",
    "text": " sand.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "10",
    "text": "They make fun of kings and princes ",
    "add": "of other countries",
    "text": "of other countries",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and they ridicule all the cities that have high walls around them.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "They pile dirt ",
    "add": "outside those walls",
    "text": "outside those walls",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "in order to climb up",
    "text": "in order to climb up",
    "text": " and capture those cities.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "11",
    "text": "They rush past like the wind,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and then they go ",
    "add": "to attack other cities",
    "text": "to attack other cities",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "But they are very guilty,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "because ",
    "add": "they think that",
    "text": "they think that",
    "text": " their own power is their god.\u201D",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "Habakkuk\u2019s second complaint",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "12",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "Then I said,",
    "text": "Then I said,",
    "text": " \u201CYahweh, you have certainly [RHQ] always/forever been God.",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "You are my Holy One; you will not die.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "So ",
    "add": "why",
    "text": "why",
    "text": " have you appointed those men ",
    "add": "from Babylonia",
    "text": "from Babylonia",
    "text": " to judge and get rid of ",
    "add": "us",
    "text": "us",
    "text": "?",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "You are like [MET] a huge rock ",
    "add": "under which we are protected/safe",
    "text": "under which we are protected/safe",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "so why have you sent them to punish us?",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "13",
    "text": "You [SYN] are pure, and you cannot endure looking at what is evil,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "so why ",
    "text": "so why ",
    "text": " are you ignoring men who are treacherous?",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Why do you do nothing",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "to punish",
    "text": "to punish",
    "text": " those wicked men ",
    "add": "from Babylonia",
    "text": "from Babylonia",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "who destroy people who are more righteous than they ",
    "add": "are",
    "text": "are",
    "text": "?",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "14",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "Do you consider that",
    "text": "Do you consider that",
    "text": " we are like fish in the sea,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "or like other creatures in the sea, that have no ruler?",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "15",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "The soldiers of Babylonia think that we are fish",
    "text": "The soldiers of Babylonia think that we are fish",
    "text": " [RHQ] for them to pull out of the sea with hooks",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "or to catch in their nets,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "while they rejoice and celebrate.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "16",
    "text": "If they catch us, they will ",
    "add": "worship",
    "text": "worship",
    "text": " their weapons [MET] with which they captured us, and offer sacrifices to them",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and burn incense in front of them!",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "They will say",
    "text": "They will say",
    "text": " \u2018Those weapons have enabled us to become rich and be able to eat expensive food.\u2019",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "17",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "Will you allow",
    "text": "Will you allow",
    "text": " them to continue ",
    "add": "to conquer people",
    "text": "to conquer people",
    "text": " [MET] forever?",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "Will you allow",
    "text": "Will you allow",
    "text": " them to destroy people of other nations without their being merciful ",
    "add": "to anyone",
    "text": "to anyone",
    "text": "?\u201D",
    "c": "2",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "After I said that, I said to myself,",
    "text": "After I said that, I said to myself,",
    "text": " \u201CI will climb up into my watchtower,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and stand there at my guard post.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "I will wait there to find out what Yahweh will say,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "what he will reply to what I have complained about.\u201D",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "Yahweh\u2019s second reply",
    "style": "p",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "2",
    "text": "Then Yahweh replied to me,",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\u201CWrite plainly on tablets ",
    "add": "what I am revealing to you in",
    "text": "what I am revealing to you in",
    "text": " this vision,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "and then read it to a messenger",
    "text": "and then read it to a messenger",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "in order that he can run with it ",
    "add": "to tell it to",
    "text": "to tell it to",
    "text": " other people.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "3",
    "text": "In this vision ",
    "add": "I will be talking about things that will happen",
    "text": "I will be talking about things that will happen",
    "text": " in the future.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Now is not the time when those things will happen,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "but they certainly will happen,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and when they occur, they will occur quickly,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and they will not be delayed.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Now you ",
    "add": "want those things to happen immediately, but",
    "text": "want those things to happen immediately, but",
    "text": " they are not happening.",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "But wait patiently for them ",
    "add": "to happen",
    "text": "to happen",
    "text": "!",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "4",
    "text": "Think about the proud ",
    "add": "people of Babylonia",
    "text": "people of Babylonia",
    "text": "!",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "They are certainly not doing what is righteous.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "But people who are righteous will live",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "because they faithfully ",
    "add": "do what I want them to do",
    "text": "do what I want them to do",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "5",
    "text": "If people ",
    "add": "trust in their wealth",
    "text": "trust in their wealth",
    "text": ", they will deceive themselves,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and proud people are never able to rest.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "It is as though",
    "text": "It is as though",
    "text": " the greedy people ",
    "add": "of Babylonia open their mouths",
    "text": "of Babylonia open their mouths",
    "text": " as wide as the place where dead people are,",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "and they never have enough,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "like ",
    "add": "the place where",
    "text": "the place where",
    "text": " dead people go never has enough dead people [PRS].",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "The ",
    "add": "armies of Babylonia",
    "text": "armies of Babylonia",
    "text": " conquer many nations for themselves,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and capture all their people.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "6",
    "text": "But ",
    "add": "soon",
    "text": "soon",
    "text": " all those ",
    "add": "whom they have captured",
    "text": "whom they have captured",
    "text": " will ridicule ",
    "add": "the soldiers from Babylonia",
    "text": "the soldiers from Babylonia",
    "text": "!",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "They will make fun of them, saying,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\u2018Terrible things will happen to you who have stolen things ",
    "add": "from other countries",
    "text": "from other countries",
    "text": "!",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "You got many things by forcing people to give them to you.",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "But you certainly will not keep those things",
    "text": "But you certainly will not keep those things",
    "text": " for a long time [RHQ]!\u2019",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "7",
    "text": "Suddenly those whom you \u25C4oppressed/treated cruelly\u25BA will cause you to tremble,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and they will take away all the things that you have stolen from them.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "8",
    "text": "You stole things from the people of many nations.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "You murdered [MTY] people of many people-groups,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and you destroyed their land and their cities.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "So those who are still alive will steal valuable things from you.",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "9",
    "text": "Terrible things will happen to you ",
    "add": "people of Babylonia",
    "text": "people of Babylonia",
    "text": " who build big houses",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "with money that you got by forcing others to give it to you.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "You are proud and you think that your houses will be safe",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "because you have built them in places where you can easily defend them.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "10",
    "text": "But because you have destroyed others,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "you have caused your family [MTY] to be shamed/disgraced,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and you yourselves will be killed.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "11",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "It is as though",
    "text": "It is as though",
    "text": " the stones in the walls ",
    "add": "of your houses",
    "text": "of your houses",
    "text": " cry out to accuse you,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and ",
    "add": "it is as though",
    "text": "it is as though",
    "text": " the beams ",
    "add": "in your ceilings",
    "text": "in your ceilings",
    "text": " also say the same things.",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "12",
    "text": "Terrible things will happen to you ",
    "add": "people of Babylonia",
    "text": "people of Babylonia",
    "text": " who kill people [MTY] in order to build cities,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "cities that you build by using money that you have gotten by committing crimes.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "13",
    "text": "But the Commander of the armies of angels has [RHQ] declared that everything that is built by people who do things like that ",
    "add": "will be destroyed by",
    "text": "will be destroyed by",
    "text": " fire;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "they will have worked hard uselessly.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "14",
    "text": "But ",
    "add": "in contrast",
    "text": "in contrast",
    "text": ", like [SIM] the oceans are filled with water,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "the earth will be filled with ",
    "add": "people who",
    "text": "people who",
    "text": " know that Yahweh is very great.",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "15",
    "text": "Terrible things will happen to you ",
    "add": "people of Babylonia",
    "text": "people of Babylonia",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "who cause people who live in nearby countries to become drunk.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "You force them to drink a lot of wine from wineskins",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "until they are drunk and then they walk around",
    "text": "until they are drunk and then they walk around",
    "text": " naked,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "in order that you can see that.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "16",
    "text": "But you are the ones who ",
    "add": "soon",
    "text": "soon",
    "text": " will be disgraced instead of being honored.",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "It will be as though you are forced to",
    "text": "It will be as though you are forced to",
    "text": " drink ",
    "add": "a lot of wine",
    "text": "a lot of wine",
    "text": " in order that you will also stagger ",
    "add": "around, drunk",
    "text": "around, drunk",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "You will drink the wine ",
    "add": "that symbolizes that Yahweh will punish you",
    "text": "that symbolizes that Yahweh will punish you",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and he will cause you to be disgraced instead of being greatly respected ",
    "add": "any more",
    "text": "any more",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "17",
    "text": "You did violent [PRS] things to ",
    "add": "the people in",
    "text": "the people in",
    "text": " Lebanon,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and you killed the wild animals ",
    "add": "there",
    "text": "there",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "but you will be punished severely for doing that.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "You have killed [MTY] many people",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "and you have destroyed their lands and their cities.",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "18",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "You people of Babylonia need to know that your",
    "text": "You people of Babylonia need to know that your",
    "text": " idols are completely [RHQ] useless,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "because it is people who made them.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Statues that have been carved or made in a mold deceive you.",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "Those who trust in idols",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "are trusting in things that they themselves created,",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "things that cannot speak!",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "19",
    "text": "Terrible things will happen to you who say to lifeless idols that are made of wood,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\u2018Wake up!\u2019",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Idols certainly cannot [RHQ] tell you what you should do;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "they ",
    "add": "look nice/beautiful because",
    "text": "look nice/beautiful because",
    "text": " they are covered with silver and gold,",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "but they are not alive.",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "20",
    "text": "But Yahweh is in his holy temple;",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "everyone on the earth should be silent in his presence.\u201D",
    "c": "3",
    "style": "s1",
    "text": "A prayer sung by Habakkuk",
    "style": "p",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "1-2",
    "text": "Yahweh, I have heard about you;",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "I revere you because of ",
    "add": "all the amazing",
    "text": "all the amazing",
    "text": " things that you have done.",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "In our time, do again ",
    "add": "some of",
    "text": "some of",
    "text": " those things that you did long ago!",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "Even when you are angry ",
    "add": "with us",
    "text": "with us",
    "text": ",",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "be merciful ",
    "add": "to us",
    "text": "to us",
    "text": "!",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "3",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "In the vision, I saw",
    "text": "In the vision, I saw",
    "text": " God, the Holy One, coming from the Teman ",
    "add": "district in Edom",
    "text": "district in Edom",
    "text": ";",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "and I also saw",
    "text": "and I also saw",
    "text": " him coming from the Paran Hills ",
    "add": "in the Sinai area",
    "text": "in the Sinai area",
    "text": ".",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "His glory filled the sky,",
