    "text": "The hills and mountains that have existed for a very long time [HYP] collapsed and crumbled.",
    "style": "q2",
    "text": "Yahweh is the one who exists eternally/forever!",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "7",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "add": "In the vision",
    "text": "In the vision",
    "text": " I saw the ",
