    "text": "and the people in the Midian ",
    "add": "region",
    "text": "region",
    "text": " trembling.",
    "style": "b",
    "style": "q1",
    "text": "\n    ",
    "v": "8",
    "text": "Yahweh, was it because you were angry with the rivers and streams that you were angry with them?",
